ync" class="size-full wp-image-3230799" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1.jpg" alt="海莉·清子" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Hayley-Kiyoko-FTG-Press-Photo-6-Credit-Trevor-Flores-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3230799" class="wp-caption-text">海莉·清子，2022 年。图片来源：Trevor Flores。</figcaption></figure><p> “我们将继续创造空间，点燃希望。感谢每一位合作者和朋友，从音乐视频开始及以后一直为我提供帮助的人。”</p><p> “我从心底里感谢你们。感谢您出现在我身边，提醒我我并不孤单。我太激动了，终于能与大家分享这个消息，让这部电影成为现实。”</p><p> Kiyoko 还计划于 2025 年出版她的第二部小说《 <em>Where There&#39;s Room For Us</em> 》。她的最新专辑《Panorama》于 2022 年发行，次年她发行了两首单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-kiyoko-returns-with-vibrant-new-single-greenlight-3449006">《Greenlight》</a>和《Somewhere Between the sand and the stardust》 。</p><p>海莉·清子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-kiyoko-to-make-directorial-debut-with-girls-like-girls-film-3818997">(Hayley Kiyoko) 执导的电影《Girls Like Girls》</a>首次亮相于<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> 。</p> ;
