nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_chappellroan_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Chappell-Roan">Chappell Roan</a>分享了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify Wrapped</a>成绩， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heart">Heart</a> 1977 年的热门单曲《Barracuda》成为她当年收听次数最多的歌曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024">2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>在昨天（12 月 4 日）分享的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDKiHzcyxv4/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>帖子中，可以看到年轻的罗恩在一辆贴有迷彩贴花和大量牛角的汽车旁边摆姿势。 “这张照片有点疯狂，”她在标题中写道。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">这位前<em>NME</em>封面</a>明星还透露了 Spotify Wrapped 列出的年度最佳五位艺术家。这家流媒体巨头的年度专题节目已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-wrapped-2024-launches-how-to-see-yours-and-the-biggest-tracks-and-artists-of-the-year-3818688">成为音乐爱好者这个节日期间的主要内容</a>——在“庆祝您的一年”体验中反映了他们过去 12 个月的收听习惯。</p><p>对于 Roan 来说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/chappell-roan-live-in-london-a-joyous-celebration-of-queerness-community-and-fun-3795515">她自己在 2024 年也经历了一个里程碑</a>，她透露今年最受听的五位艺术家是——从一到五——Ariana <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Grande</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、Heart、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kacey-musgraves">Kacey Musgraves</a> 。</p><p> “最受欢迎的歌曲是 Barracuda ofc，”她写道，指的是硬摇滚乐队的标志性单曲。 Roan <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-chappell-roans-fiery-cover-of-hearts-barracuda-3799795">曾在 10 月份的最近一次美国巡演中翻唱过这首歌</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDKiHzcyxv4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,7